==English==
===Noun===
'''arytenoid'''
#{{anatomy}} either of a pair of movable [[cartilage]]s in the [[larynx]] that serve as posterior attachment points for the vocal folds; a [[muscle]] attached to this cartilage, or a [[gland]] located near it
===Adjective===
'''arytenoid'''
# of, or relating to this cartilage, muscle or gland
